Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Why didn't you attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the Mirror Knights are controlling them, this is all part of Dartz's scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we lose now, neither their future or the future of the world will hold any meaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! The third barrier of the Orichalcos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You said you're going to activate its true power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Third Barrier of Orichalcos"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Tritos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including this card, the Barrier of Orichalcos has now been fully completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third barrier of the Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And due to the effects of Orichalcos Deuteros,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regain some of my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz's Life just went up again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Diablos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Ability, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Power of Orichalcos Diablos pressures pressures Defender Monsters into switching into Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Orichalcos Diablos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's attacked like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's Life will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card activate! Shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Tritos - its power nullifies all Magic and Trap Cards used against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, your tricks will no longer work against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It increases the Attack Power of all Monsters and increases the player's Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it negates both Traps and Magics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's truly an impregnable barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Diablos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Element of Cry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambush Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tribute Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That 2600 points of Defense Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be added to the Attack Power of Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twilight Zone's Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stronger than his Monster's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbow Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Orichalcos Kyutora's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we raise our Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we can't damage him as long as that absorption Monster stays on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually wasted your own Monster to save Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the "power of bonds" you people talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a result of that Trap just now, Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have lost the only Monster you had to act as your protective shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall allow you to have a special reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mirror Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the three layers of the Orichalcos Barrier, you will be unable to resist me any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squirm, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is now time to use the nameless card I entrusted to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless card...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden within this room is a new card I have created!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card we got back then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That one card holds within it the power needed to break the seal on the Legendary Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seal on the Legendary Dragons...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Knight Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More importantly, the nameless card Pegasus spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did add the card among my deck after getting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But by breaking the seal on the Legendary Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did he mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will place two cards face-down and put an end to my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Seto. This will be your final draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But just like he said, I've only got 600 Life Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to find a way to turn this around on this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or I'm going to lose for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I... going to lose in a dump like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You said that you would be able to save your brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you really save him? Your little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amelda... The future you entrusted me with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my own road of glory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let it all end in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch my Duel closely and burn it in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! It's come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one card in my deck that can turn this around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you've had a set card on the field that you've yet to activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I know you as well as I think, it has to be Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to awaken that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias! Fuse yourself with Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Force Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Force Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, as long as those Mirror Knights stay on the field, we can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse to sever the ties you have with your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll sever them for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Force Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Mirror Knight Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! Pegasus still has his Mirror Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Big Brother specifically chose him {\i1}because{\i0} he still has a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Mirror Force Dragon's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The energy he shot back...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's being absorbed by Mirror Force Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Ability of Mirror Force Dragon takes all damage sent towards it and redirects it towards every Monster on my opponent's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll all be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd really slay your comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "darkness of the heart" you keep going on and on about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Mokuba have seen it throughout or entire lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness in our hearts that we ignored and ignored some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until our hearts were nearly pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've surpassed it and come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've carved out the light that exists in our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we've got that, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those four are really True Duelists, they should have no regrets disappearing right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reduce them all to nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Force Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genocide Big Bang!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!! Guys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're okay with this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I have underestimated you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as Orichalcos Kyutora is before us to absorb all damage sent my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Special Ability of yours can be tamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's lost all his Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that is accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Orichalcos Kyutora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal onto us your true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is... that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the evolved form of Orichalcos Kyutora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Shunoros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos... Shunoros?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack Power is determined by the total points of damage absorbed by Orichalcos Kyutora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Attack Power of Orichalcos Shunoros is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20000!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, no matter {\i1}how{\i0} you slice it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys{\i0} were the ones who created this being!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Monster born from your malice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it goes by the name of Orichalcos Shunoros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From our hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shunoros' Attack Power will go down each time it battles against a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate Orichalcos Shunoros' Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Dexia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Aristeros!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Dexia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be be destroyed so long as Shunoros remains on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack Power is equal to the Attack or Defense Points of a Monster it battles with plus 300 additional points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the ultimate sword of Shunoros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Aristeros...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also cannot be destroyed so long as Shunoros remains on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will always hold 300 more points than the opponent's Attack Power, so it is capable of withstanding all attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the ultimate shield of Shunoros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the two have been activated...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shunoros will be untouched by any and all attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moreover, Shunoros is virtually untouchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And unless we can destroy the two in the front, our attacks will never even {\i0}reach{\i1} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall proceed to invoke a Trap I had face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of the Martyrs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card launches whenever one of my cards on the field is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seals away the Effects of my enemy's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It then forces a Monster of my choice into unavoidable battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I will select to partake in battle is naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Force Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Effect of Mirror Force Dragon will be unable to reach Shunoros.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time you will truly meet your demise, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Shunoros will engage in attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Ring!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acti...vate...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope After Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever one of my Monsters is destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Attack Power of that Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is... added to your Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've... paid you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step over my corpse... and go forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, become an offering to my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ye empty shell of a body holding no soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes, Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how loudly you may weep, your voice shall never reach Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Seto's soul no longer resides in the being lying beside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...! My brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return my brother's soul right {\i1}now{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God's voice rains over the heavens with joy at having received Seto's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you offer my brother's soul to {\i1}no one{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of those lying there are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by doing this, you have lost the remaining comrades you had to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you the final piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that I seek to destroy the present world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason behind this, Nameless Pharaoh, lies with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose it is you were resurrected after a 3,000-year slumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is reason behind all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you know about my lost past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a city in Ancient Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... me, 3,000 years ago...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a serious crime to damage this sacred temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice is in the name of the Gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the name of the God is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Three Hidden Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}iron{\i0} fist of a {\i1}God{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Hand Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3,000 years ago in Ancient Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the seal on "Duel Monsters" was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those with darkness in their hearts began to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once again, people began to wallow in the darkness of their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jut as what happened to me 10,000 years ago in Atlantis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I must awaken the Orichalcos God and lay this world to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is what led this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the vision of Ancient Egypt the Millennium Puzzle showed me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, back then, those with darkness in their hearts went on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus it was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... destroyed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after 3,000 years of passing, another surprising event occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, a powerful soul who controlled the darkness in his heart was reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cursed soul in turn attracted others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cursed soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Nameless Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it you have come back after all these years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is but one answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is because you yourself defy history!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you are a hateful king who carries with him a vile fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, your main purpose is to congregate the darkness of the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. You yourself are the source! The darkness in the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are destined to be the end of this 10,000-year span of history after your sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} down, and Yugi fighting all by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz claims, "You are the cause for this world's destruction."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faced with unimaginable pressure from his unbeatable strategy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi is pushed into a desperate corner and begins losing the will to fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! We have to save Yugi somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The nameless card Pegasus gave Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe with that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Revive! The Three Legendary Warriors"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:23:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
